    {
      "id": "9adffdf1_253161a2",
      "file_path": "hv-collector-core/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/impl/MessageValidator.kt",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 30,
      "message": "I'd prefer to have this class non-rx. Maybe return Either<String(nok), String(ok)> or Optional<errormessage> in both cases. Having utility function in utils module, we can simply use it on a result from current class in VesHvCollector class.",
